articles.description: Payton Pritchard had 19 points and 10 assists, and Troy Brown Jr. also had a double-double to lead Oregon past Washington State 84-57 on Sunday night.

videos.description: UConn's Antwoine Anderson picks up a loose ball and puts it back up to get the basket and the foul.
videos.headline: Hustle leads to UConn and-1

videos.description: Michigan State's Miles Bridges drives to the hoop, and can't get his first shot to go, but tips in his own miss for the score.
videos.headline: Bridges scores with second effort

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Huskies guard Jalen Adams sizes up his man and rises up to hit the shot from deep.
videos.headline: UConn's Adams drains 3-pointer from NBA range

videos.description: Michigan State freshman Jaren Jackson Jr. takes a pass at the top of the key and uses the backboard to get the shot to fall.
videos.headline: Jackson banks it in for Spartans 3

videos.description: Spartans big man Jaren Jackson Jr. rises up to emphatically blocks Terry Larrier's shot out of bounds.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Jackson swats shot out of bounds

videos.description: Michigan State forward Nick Ward hits the offensive glass and follows up with the hoop and the harm.
videos.headline: Spartans' Ward grabs offensive board, gets putback and-1

videos.description: Jaren Jackson Jr. pulls down an offensive rebound on a missed free throw and goes back up strong to flush home a powerful dunk.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Jackson punishes the rim

videos.description: UConn forward Terry Larrier gets the ball at the end of the shot clock and hoists a shot over two defenders for the bucket.
videos.headline: Huskies' Larrier beats shot clock with contested jumper

videos.description: Alterique Gilbert breaks his man down off the dribble, gets into the lane, and finishes with a sweet finger roll.
videos.headline: UConn's Gilbert dazzles with scoop layup

videos.description: Spartans sophomore guard Cassius Winston repeatedly knocks down tough shots to extend Michigan State's lead over UConn.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Winston catches fire in second half

videos.description: Cassius Winston gets into the lane and finishes the layup to cap his great night and a Michigan State win.
videos.headline: Spartans' Winston drops career-high 28 in masterful performance
